  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b9a\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf \u0ba4\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bcd \u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Independence Party ready to form all-party government'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Maithripala Sirisena has said that the Sri Lanka Freedom Party is going to form a proper all-party government in collaboration with the Left parties.",
        "He said this while participating in an event held yesterday (28) in Maharakami. He further stated,",
        "This government is headed by budding party leaders. They have no desire to form an all-party government.",
        "Therefore, in the future, we will take steps to form a stable all-party government in collaboration with the Sri Lanka Freedom Party and the Left parties. (a)"
      ],
